examples: You can watch us via satellite on Wikistar 1 tp. 8.

senses.sense: To toilet paper; to throw toilet paper in rolls over a structure, so the structure becomes draped with it.
(tradecraft) Initialism of teeth per inch — a measure used on saw blades
(computing) Initialism of tracks per inch — a measure of disk capacity
(cycling) Initialism of threads per inch — a measure of the density of threads in screwable parts (e.g. bottom brackets).
